quran[30]{c,v,t,f}:
  74,37,"Kwa jwalijose mwa jenumanja jwaasachile kuti alongolele (pakutenda yambone) kapena kusigalila (pakupanganya yakusakala)."
  74,38,"Mundu jwalijose tachiŵa uwombosi wakuliombolela ku (yakusakala) yaŵapanganyisye (pakutaŵidwa ku Moto)."
  74,39,"Ikaŵeje aŵala ŵakunkono wan'dyo."
  75,34,"Chonasiko nichenu! Chonasiko chisyene!"
  75,35,"Soni chonasiko nichenu! Chonasiko chisyene!"
  75,36,"Ana jukuganichisya mundu yanti chijugambe kulechedwa wambape (ngapedwa malamusi soni ngaja kulipidwa)?"
  76,28,"Uwwe ni ŵatwaagumbile ŵanganyao soni twaliyiye kagumbidwe kao, soni tuli tusachile mpaka tuiche nao ŵane ŵanti mpela ŵanganyao kwinjila m’malo mwao (nambo ali ŵakun'jogopa Allah)."
  76,29,"Chisimu galakwe (ma Ȃyaga) gaŵele chikumbusyo, basi jwaakusaka aliikolochesye chilepe litala lyakuujila kwa M'bujegwe (Allah)."
  76,30,"Ni nganim'ba nsachile ŵanganyammwe ikaŵeje akasache kaje Allah, chisimu Allah aŵele Jwakumanyilila nnope, Jwalunda lwakusokoka."
  77,25,"Ana nganituliŵika litaka kuŵa chikuti?"
  77,26,"Cha ŵachijumi ni ŵawe?"
  77,27,"Ni tuŵisile mwalakwemo yakunyichisya yaileu-leu (gagali matumbi), ni tumpele kumwa ŵanganyammwe mesi gakunong’a."
  78,22,"Kwa ŵakusumba mpika gaŵele malo gakuujila."
  78,23,"Tachiŵa nkutama mwalakwemo yaka-yaka."
  78,24,"Ngasapasya mwalakwemo kusisimila namuno yakumwa (yakumasya njota)."
  79,16,"Pandema jaŵam'bilaasile Ambujegwe (Allah) pachiŵata chakutakata (chakuŵilanjikwa) Tuwaa."
  79,17,"(Nikuntenda kuti): Jaawulani kwa Firiauna, chisimu jwalakwejo jusumbile mpika."
  79,18,"Ni nkajile: “Ana nkusaka kuti n'diiswejesye?”"
  80,13,"(Jili) mu ikalakala yakuchimbichikwa."
  80,14,"Yapenani, yakuswejesyedwa."
  80,15,"Ili m’makono mwa akulemba (Achimalaika)."
  81,10,"Ni ndema jaichipindikulidwa ikalakala (mugalembedwe masengo gamundu)."
  81,11,"Ni ndema jalichitandukulidwa liwunde."
  81,12,"Ni ndema jauchikwisilidwa Moto Waukali."
  82,4,"Ni ndema jagachiukulidwa malembe."
  82,5,"Mundu jwalijose juchimanyilila yajwalongwesye (kupanganya) ni yajwalesile munyuma."
  82,6,"E mmwe amundu! Ana ni chichi chinnyenjile kwa (kwikanila kunnyosya) M’mbuje gwenu (Allah) Jwantuka wejinji?"
  83,1,"Ipotesi ni yao ŵakupuungusya (miliingo)."
  83,2,"Aŵala ŵaakutiji naga ndema jaakulilinjila ku ŵandu (pakwasuma indu yao) akasaligumbachisyaga."
  83,3,"Nambo pa ndema jaakwaaliinjila (ŵanduo) kapena kwapimila (pakwasumisya indu) akupungusyaga."